Overview
This is a simple BMI Calculator web application that allows users to calculate their Body Mass Index (BMI) based on their weight (in kilograms) and height (in meters). The BMI value is calculated using the standard formula:
The application provides feedback about the BMI category (e.g., Underweight, Normal weight, Overweight, Obesity) based on the calculated value.
Features
Input Fields: Allows users to input their weight (in kg) and height (in meters).
Calculate Button: After entering values, users can click the "Calculate BMI" button to compute their BMI.
Category Display: Once the BMI is calculated, the app shows the BMI value along with the corresponding category (Underweight, Normal weight, Overweight, Obesity).
Responsive Layout: The application is designed to work on any screen size and is fully responsive.
